comments: Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Dosunmu (CHI) and absorbs the contact during the pick.

comments: Replay review of the OOB called on VanVleet (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. VanVleet lost the ball on his own and was the last to make contact with it before it went OOB.
